=== Etymology ===
By the way of the [[Hindi]] word ''pajama'', originally from the [[Persian]] words &#1662;&#1575;&#1610;&#1580;&#1575;&#1605;&#1607; ''p&aelig;'' / ''Payjama'' meaning "leg garment."

===Noun===
'''pyjamas''' ''plural''
#[[Clothes]] for wearing to bed and sleeping in, usually consisting of a loose-fitting shirt and trousers.

